My Android phone opens my garage door when I approach my house on my
motorcycle.

Background blog posts:

1) http://brad.livejournal.com/2394220.html

2) http://brad.livejournal.com/2394707.html

To use this, you need both the app on your phone, as well as the server
in your house to actually open the garage door, with the necessary X10
hardware.  See server/README-hardware.txt for details.
